                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="67671" author="panda" created="Thu, 26 Sep 2013 11:33:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, Emoly. Please, reopen if the problem reoccurs in the future.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="67666" author="emoly.liu" created="Thu, 26 Sep 2013 11:28:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Andrew, you are right. Sorry to reopen this one.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="67664" author="emoly.liu" created="Thu, 26 Sep 2013 10:54:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I searched Maloo test results in this link &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/query?utf8=&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/query?utf8=&lt;/a&gt;&#10003;&amp;amp;test_set%5Btest_set_script_id%5D=f6a12204-32c3-11e0-a61c-52540025f9ae&amp;amp;sub_test%5Bsub_test_script_id%5D=fb022be0-32c3-11e0-a61c-52540025f9ae&amp;amp;sub_test%5Bstatus%5D=FAIL&amp;amp;sub_test%5Bquery_bugs%5D=&amp;amp;test_session%5Btest_host%5D=&amp;amp;test_session%5Btest_group%5D=&amp;amp;test_session%5Buser_id%5D=&amp;amp;test_session%5Bquery_date%5D=&amp;amp;test_session%5Bquery_recent_period%5D=&amp;amp;test_node%5Bos_type_id%5D=&amp;amp;test_node%5Bdistribution_type_id%5D=&amp;amp;test_node%5Barchitecture_type_id%5D=&amp;amp;test_node%5Bfile_system_type_id%5D=00437f32-318d-11e1-9c6d-5254004bbbd3&amp;amp;test_node%5Blustre_branch_id%5D=&amp;amp;test_node_network%5Bnetwork_type_id%5D=&amp;amp;commit=Update+results&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I didn&apos;t check each one. Maybe you are right, their parent commit is earlier than &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3669&quot; title=&quot;(mdt_xattr.c:178:mdt_getxattr()) ASSERTION( lu_object_assert_exists(&amp;amp;info-&amp;gt;mti_object-&amp;gt;mot_obj) ) failed:&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3669&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3669&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; fix. If so, please close this ticket and ignore my previous comments.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="67662" author="panda" created="Thu, 26 Sep 2013 10:20:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The fixes were landed on Sep, 11 (see &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7208/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7208/&lt;/a&gt;), not two months ago.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s not clear whether your reports are based on sources more recent than of that date.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/5bb89698-1a4f-11e3-a95b-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/5bb89698-1a4f-11e3-a95b-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt; was ran on Sep 10.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/243e1cd2-24f0-11e3-839b-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/243e1cd2-24f0-11e3-839b-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt; was ran on Sep 23, the build links to &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7584/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7584/&lt;/a&gt;, which appears to be Patch Set 8 or earlier (Patch set 9 was uploaded on Sep 25) and the parent commit for Patch set 8 is c0e6982b57319e5044cf12bee509c0c571a17cc5, which was landed on Aug 7.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="67656" author="emoly.liu" created="Thu, 26 Sep 2013 08:31:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I reopen this ticket because through investigation on &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3625&quot; title=&quot;Test failure on test suite replay-single, subtest test_58c&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3625&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3625&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, I find still many  zfs tests hit this error in recent two months, such as:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b278ad30-24ac-11e3-93a0-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b278ad30-24ac-11e3-93a0-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/243e1cd2-24f0-11e3-839b-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/243e1cd2-24f0-11e3-839b-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/54b1a140-22e3-11e3-9488-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/54b1a140-22e3-11e3-9488-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/5bb89698-1a4f-11e3-a95b-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/5bb89698-1a4f-11e3-a95b-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&quot;No such attribute&quot; happens much more frequently than &quot;No such file or directory&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="66490" author="utopiabound" created="Thu, 12 Sep 2013 14:20:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is verified fixed by &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3669&quot; title=&quot;(mdt_xattr.c:178:mdt_getxattr()) ASSERTION( lu_object_assert_exists(&amp;amp;info-&amp;gt;mti_object-&amp;gt;mot_obj) ) failed:&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3669&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3669&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; closure&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="65072" author="pjones" created="Mon, 26 Aug 2013 16:27:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Nathaniel&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please verify whether this is still an issue after &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3669&quot; title=&quot;(mdt_xattr.c:178:mdt_getxattr()) ASSERTION( lu_object_assert_exists(&amp;amp;info-&amp;gt;mti_object-&amp;gt;mot_obj) ) failed:&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3669&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3669&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; fix has landed&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Peter&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="64763" author="panda" created="Wed, 21 Aug 2013 17:25:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The first (ZFS) report is a duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3713&quot; title=&quot;Failure on test suite sanity test_17k: get_xattr_names: llistxattr failed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3713&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3713&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; which is fixed by &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/7208&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/7208&lt;/a&gt; in the context of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3669&quot; title=&quot;(mdt_xattr.c:178:mdt_getxattr()) ASSERTION( lu_object_assert_exists(&amp;amp;info-&amp;gt;mti_object-&amp;gt;mot_obj) ) failed:&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3669&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3669&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The second report does not look xattr cache related (no traces of xattr operations either in the MDS or in the client debug logs), &quot;No such file or directory&quot; probably relates to the fact that there was no such file or directory, rather than an xattr failure.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="64758" author="adilger" created="Wed, 21 Aug 2013 17:05:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This looks like it also failed on non-zfs testing:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/749022be-07dd-11e3-bcfa-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/749022be-07dd-11e3-bcfa-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;and the first failure was on 2013-07-29 00:48:20 UTC&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/e2333076-f87a-11e2-a8b3-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/e2333076-f87a-11e2-a8b3-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;and according to &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/5537&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/5537&lt;/a&gt; the xattr cache patch landed on 07-29 also.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
